item.title: 23 September 2020
item.description: In the spirit of my “fall semester”, I here place my homework. Don’t suppose it is of public interest, but it can’t hurt to put it out there. Greek I reset the 900+ items in my Hansen and Quinn list in Studies, and took on 100 of them tonight. Only did one of the Chapter 10 exercises, #4. Will have to attend to more of them tomorrow. C++ Did exercise 51 from Chapter 7.
